  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Mucosal eosinophilia (eos/hpf)</measure>
    <time_frame>Duration of funding, approximately 5 years</time_frame>
    <description>Mucosal eosinophil levels are measured as eosinophils per high power field (eos/hpf). The primary outcome measure is to determine the change in mucosal eosinophil level (eos/hpf) and to determine if the change in mucosal eosinophil level in eos/hpf correlates with other measures of disease activity.</description>
